thirtyfive.title: 180118 [TF01073]
thirtyfive.artist: FFI DIGITAL
tags: another thing no one will like
thirtyfive.about: 180118 was originally intended to be a 9-disc box set on Inner Demons Records. Then shipping costs skyrocketed, and box sets became unfeasible. Then I was gonna release it as a series of single- or double- 3" disc sets, but I didn't like the idea of having that many similar releases. So here it is.

thirtyfive.title: RUBBER THOUGHTS AND THEIR EFFECT ON FOCUS VOL. 1 [TF01210]
thirtyfive.artist: THIS IS WHAT I HEAR WHEN YOU TALK
thirtyfive.about: This album is created all by the same pedal chain. The first track has one delay, and each subsequent track adds one additional delay to the line. For multi-function pedals, only the delay portions were used. The sound source was a drum machine run through a reverb, distortion, and 2 noise gates. The saturation effect on the Maw was also used.
